{"tid":1387560,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"烏克蘭鏡子革命 其實香港行得通","createTime":"2019-07-30T14:30:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T14:39:52.000Z","uid":89679,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4c5a8bbd1c13b56cc33b8363b77bd7d878874dd7","tid":1387560,"uid":89679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:30:03.000Z","msg":"(唔好意思, 第一次發帖, 唔啱規距的話請通知)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EtmeKSU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEtmeKSU.jpg&h=4dd4108c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廢老一名, 剩係識和理非非. FB見到有人講 &quot;烏克蘭鏡子革命&quot;, 覺得幾有意思. 可以畀返班差佬嘅惡型惡相自己睇返. 不過普遍有人話啲鏡會碎, 會成為攻擊性武器云云.<br />\n我哋呢啲怕死嘅死廢老, 當然想達到0%被捕, 0%受傷啦. 最後, 畀我搵一搵, 搵到IKEA有種不碎兒童鏡, 只係39蚊, 用阿卡歷膠 (即硬膠膠), 應該安全. 大家不妨考慮下次夢遊時拎去照妖.<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ikea.com.hk/zh/products/children's-ikea/children-(8-14)/children's-accessories-(8-14)/drommare-art-30256792?fbclid=IwAR12KBlK6fjBQC4HCmDSztKAdWNjt4uIXav_URSW28Czw3BVPTs9LK5VwIg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ikea.com.hk%2Fzh%2Fproducts%2Fchildren%27s-ikea%2Fchildren-%288-14%29%2Fchildren%27s-accessories-%288-14%29%2Fdrommare-art-30256792%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR12KBlK6fjBQC4HCmDSztKAdWNjt4uIXav_URSW28Czw3BVPTs9LK5VwIg&d=RNMQoofY58y8BAaKNkwZNi8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=925338b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ikea.com.hk/zh/products/children's-ikea/children-(8-14)/children's-accessories-(8-14)/drommare-art-30256792?fbclid=IwAR12KBlK6fjBQC4HCmDSztKAdWNjt4uIXav_URSW28Czw3BVPTs9LK5VwIg</a><br />\n<br />\n請多多指教"},{"pid":"d6b09684f28d4f2c18d497d07866f68fac81cb1c","tid":1387560,"uid":279159,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:32:49.000Z","msg":"2014講過<br />\n無用<br />\n腦已洗"},{"pid":"8afb2afffcae338fd2c5d52f125d904c945beeb3","tid":1387560,"uid":47758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:33:33.000Z","msg":"日頭都有少少用，但夜晚啲畜龍防暴遮鳩哂自己個樣，佢哋自己都冇眼睇自己"},{"pid":"214c899dced875fa0fc818a15d27b6e884a81cbf","tid":1387560,